title: 'Excellent Piece of furniture for a wonderful price'
body: It came well packed. Looks beautiful. Although minor scratches are visible on top surface and sides. I called a electrician and we both read the chart and some figuring out on our own. As he keep doing this assembling furniture work in the society so he had a pretty good idea how to assemble it. It had some pretty complex type of screws that I would not have figured out myself. Paid him Rs.200 for the job. Yes only required quantity of screws and assembling stuff was given. We were luck that we didn't spoil any. I would recommend to provide more extra stuff to assemble it. All said and done. Excellent piece of furniture for a wonderful price. Just don't sit on it as it's made of board and don't move it too much. Loved it Cheers!!! Anurag

title: 'Product matches the price.'
body: It arrives in a padded box (yet there might be some minor scrapes on the edges) The pieces are well labelled and screws provided along with an easy to follow instructions manual.
